pace":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"3233218577","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3233218577","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzIzMzIxODU3Nw==","status":"current","title":"VPos","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":10592077},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3233218577/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3233218577/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3233218577/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3233218577/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3233218577","tinyui":"/x/EQC3w","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3233218577","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3233218577/VPos","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3233218577"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"1c6977a5-6be1-4b11-b480-669c76dc7999\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para <a href=\"https://bancard.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/PV21/pages/782958626/VPOS+MEJORAS+UX\">VPos - Mejoras UX</a>, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"712020:9e4c7b07-03d5-4a81-a522-cc90518f3086\" ri:local-id=\"4762cc90-23f5-4a51-9123-75a9c34837cb\" /></ac:link>.</p><p>Las horas estimadas rondan entre <strong>138 y 146</strong>, dependiendo en la opci&oacute;n elegida en el m&oacute;dulo de Vista Previa del Portal.</p><p>Fecha estimada de entrega: <strong>Mi&eacute;rcoles</strong> <time datetime=\"2024-12-11\" />, comenzando: <strong>Lunes</strong> <time datetime=\"2024-11-18\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 194.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 400.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 165.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>M&oacute;dulo</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Flujo de Catastros</strong></p></td><td><p>Exploraci&oacute;n</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Traspaso de piezas del formulario CI al formulario de tarjetas</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Armado de las pre-consultas para determinar el tipo de tarjeta </p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Pruebas locales </p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Flujo de comisiones</strong></p></td><td><p>Cambios visuales del formulario de &ldquo;recibir factura por costo del servicio&rdquo; + estilizado de checkbox</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Pruebas locales</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Formulario de Pago</strong></p></td><td><p>Limitar ancho del iframe (320 a 540px, 90% de la vista siempre que se pueda) y acoplamiento de los campos en vistas mobile</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Integracion del tooltip de CVV (Falta imagen de la tarjeta para tooltip)</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Ocultar el campo cuotas si se trata de una tarjeta de cr&eacute;dito</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Pruebas</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">2</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Restricci&oacute;n de marcas de tarjeta</strong></p></td><td><p>Tabulado de las marcas disponibles para cada cliente y CRUD correspondiente</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Filtrado y desplegado de las marcas disponibles</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">6</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Mostrar siempre logos Visa y MasterCard, filtrar el resto</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Pruebas</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Vista Previa del Portal</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Opci&oacute;n 1</strong>: Renderizado de la vista en un paso posterior a la configuraci&oacute;n de colores + pruebas</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">20</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p><strong>Opci&oacute;n 2</strong>: Refactor de las configuraciones de color y simulaci&oacute;n del portal + pruebas</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">28</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Llamar el iframe usando presets o detalle de los colores via API + pruebas</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">20</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>120 - 128</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>18</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>138 - 146</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3534684161"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":179689619},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3534684161/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3534684161/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3534684161/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3534684161/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3534684161","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3534684161/VPos+-+Mejoras+UX+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3534684161","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3534684161","tinyui":"/x/AQCv0g","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}